{"tid":1826393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尹兆堅斥濫權濫捕　特首稱大部分指控不實","createTime":"2020-01-16T05:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T05:55:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b10f950a794905297eed3fa34204c7d8ba3b664","tid":1826393,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Kz6HtNVc/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FKz6HtNVc%2Fimage.jpg&h=9e8da575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/6QSjNcBV/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F6QSjNcBV%2F2.jpg&h=ee540f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅在立法會答問會表示，行政長官林鄭月娥違反承諾出賣良知出賣港人，不回應五大訴求，敵視青年，縱容警察濫暴，又說很多暴動罪檢控因為無合理證據而撤控，反映是濫權濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說尹兆堅的指控絕大部分不實，回應檢控工作時指出，在獨立司法制度中要相信公平公正的審訊，律政司決定不受干擾，亦沒有人保證每宗檢控都一定成功，否則偏離獨立，她又說執法機關嚴正執法正正是保護市民。<br />\n<br />\n她強調不會敵視年青人，相反非常愛護青年，希望不要完全抹殺政府工作。尹兆堅追問時就，代青年問林鄭月娥「幾時死」，被立法會主席梁君彥指不是議會使用的語言，林鄭月娥沒再作回應。"},{"pid":"3cf759c0b4eca9303b16381610dcb7c756c38df4","tid":1826393,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"點大部分法？有調整過？有無報告support 呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c070457e1bf29402a559c9e0dc37a4f43b43d0","tid":1826393,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cf759c0b4eca9303b16381610dcb7c756c38df4","tid":1826393,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"點大部分法？有調整過？有無報告support 呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"調查"}]}